snippet.title: Symphony Game Trailer (2012)
snippet.description:
Your music is under attack... You must liberate it! 

This is the new 2012 trailer for Symphony, the upcoming music-driven game by Empty Clip Studios. As you fight to liberate your music collection, Symphony turns the unique musical content of every one of your songs into both a unique level, and a unique item you can equip and upgrade. 

The game is scheduled for a 2012 release, with the platform and exact release date(s) still unannounced.
